    "Any study focusing on a subset of a population must define its inclusion and exclusion criteria.",
    "With this method, researchers more reliably, precisely, and objectively identify the people in their study population.",
    "Articles published in English peerreviewed journals were considered for this study, but theses, dissertations, and conference proceedings were not.",
    "The screening procedure began with the articles imported into Thomson Reuters' EndNote X8 program.",
    "Then, a web and mobile application were utilized to screen all created articles for relevance."
